headline: 2 Tech Stocks You Can Buy and Hold for the Next Decade
summary: Meta Platforms and PayPal stocks are affordably priced, especially among stocks in the tech sector.  AI investments have paid off for Meta, helping the stock outperform in recent years.  PayPal's stock has been in a slump, but new company leadership and expansion into digital advertising have the potential to stimulate growth.
